original: Zachrisson, Gustaf Ragnar, kyrkoherde, Rölanda, f. 17/6/98 i Foss, Gbgs o. Boh. 1., av C. F. o. Kristina Zachrisson. G. 28 m. Signe Rosendahl. Barn: Anna f. 28, stud., Malmö, Sven 34, Erik 36, Karin 38, Nils 41. — Stud:ex i Lund 24, teol. fil. ex. 30, teol. kand., prakt. teol. prov o. prästv. f. Karlstads stift 32. V. pastor i Rölanda 32, kyrkoh. där sed. 34. Ordf. i kyrkostämma, skolstyr., barnav:nd o. kom-m :fullm.
translated: Zachrisson, Gustaf Ragnar, clergyman, Rölanda, b. 17/6/98 in Foss, Gothenburg and Bohus County, 1st child of C.F. and Kristina Zachrisson. Married on 28th to Signe Rosendahl. Children: Anna b. 28, student, Malmö; Sven b. 34; Erik b. 36; Karin b. 38; Nils b. 41. Graduated from Lund University in 1924, obtained a Bachelor's degree in theology in 1930, completed practical theology exams and was ordained as a priest for the Diocese of Karlstad in 1932. Assistant pastor in Rölanda from 1932, appointed as parish priest in 1934. Served as chairman in the church council, school committee, childcare committee, and local government council.
